data.title: "Explain Yourself! with Jay Light" Frank Anthony Castillo (Podcast Episode 2014)
data.meta_description: Frank Anthony Castillo: With Frank Castillo, Jay Light. Check out the new episode of EXPLAIN YOURSELF. with guest, good friend, and Roast Battle DJ Frank Anthony Castillo. We talk about why you shouldn't drink the water in the Dominican Republic, where to find the best tits in Tijuana, and other important facts. Props to Hannah Jane Ayers for sitting quietly while we recorded this nonsense. Enjoy.
